    <!-- Measurement guide bottom sheet -->
    <string name="measurement_guide_title">🧭 Measurement Guide</string>
    <string name="measurement_guide_body">1. Align the ball in the center of the screen target ring and tap BALL.\n\n2. Point the camera toward the cup. Align the cup in the center of the screen target ring, then tap CUP.\n\n3. If the cup is hard to identify because it\'s far away, move toward the cup until you\'re about 5 m away, then align again and tap CUP.\n\n4. When FINAL is shown, the measurement is complete.\n\n* Recommended within 10 m.\n* Measure when Tracking is GOOD.\n* Accuracy may vary depending on grass and lighting.</string>

